:03:49.000Z","msg":"冇專利 冇錢搵 你去研發?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"藥廠由國家管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:13:36.000Z","msg":"最理想咪國家出錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:24:47.000Z","msg":"一般黎講<br />\n用自己既錢，做自己既事 = 性價比最高<br />\n用自己既錢，做人地既事 = 最平，但無質素<br />\n用人地既錢，做自己既事 = 天價<br />\n用人地既錢，做人地既事 = 天價+無質素<br />\n<br />\n國企既通病通常都第四種情況"},{"pid":"b5ab698f097267a6e01c3ca00f735bbea08e1727","tid":1019664,"uid":110892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:29:30.000Z","msg":"有無英文source"},{"pid":"19a76685cb6abdf77cf3e8cd6438b8af9881699c","tid":1019664,"uid":236404,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"I am working in drug development in Asia Pac..<br />\n<br />\n其實研發葯真係燒錢，由大學lab discovery 到第一個國家 market到，平均要十五年<br />\n<br />\n最後成功嘅 molecule 少過1% (this is based on text books stat data 啦)<br />\n<br />\n完全唔計葯廠人工，CEO 啲分紅，大學醫生,教授,nurse人工，淨係計臨床研究三期，一個病人要用五十至七十萬港紙。臨床研究三期全球通常要收症500至2000個case<br />\n<br />\n臨床三期只是drug development 嘅 Last stage... 同埋以上數字只是 South East Asia, 大部分 research 都在歐美，貴多差不多一倍。<br />\n<br />\n當然，CEO人工一定好撚高la"},{"pid":"4fd81c340fb099fa19cece611e826caf48a78782","tid":1019664,"uid":10101,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"26de0bb4709b679ae9e9323f2021f432536f5f5c","tid":1019664,"uid":33907,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cd6cf866349fd5d9e0209cbf7db596eb3cca08a4","tid":1019664,"uid":51521,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"30878ed83e6210e4fd75cc5b5e6b63830716e773","tid":1019664,"uid":37874,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"冇專利 冇錢搵 你去研發?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr